%% OAuth 2.0 Authorization Code Flow
%% Render at https://mermaid.live or in GitHub README

sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 👤 User
    participant A as 🖥️ Your App
    participant G as 🐙 GitHub
    participant API as 📡 GitHub API

    U->>A: Clicks "Login with GitHub"
    A->>G: Redirects to GitHub /authorize
    Note over A,G: client_id + scope + state + redirect_uri
    G->>U: "Authorize this app?"
    U->>G: Clicks "Yes"
    G->>A: Redirects back with ?code=abc123&state=xyz
    Note over A: Verifies state matches (CSRF check)
    A->>G: POST /access_token (code + client_secret)
    Note over A,G: Server-to-server — user doesn't see this
    G->>A: Returns access_token
    A->>API: GET /user (Bearer token)
    API->>A: Returns {name, email, avatar}
    A->>U: Shows profile page 🎉
